<template>
  <el-table
      :data="tableData"
      style="width: 100%"
  >
    <el-table-column align="center" label="ID" width="100" type="index">
    </el-table-column>

    <el-table-column
        prop="date"
        label="日期"
        width="180">
    </el-table-column>
    <el-table-column
        prop="name"
        label="姓名"
        width="180">
    </el-table-column>
    <el-table-column
        prop="address"
        label="地址">
    </el-table-column>

    <el-table-column
        label="操作"
        width="100">
      <template slot-scope="scope">
        <el-button @click="handleClick(scope.row)" type="text" size="small">查看</el-button>
      </template>
    </el-table-column>
  </el-table>
</template>

<script>
export default {

  data() {
    return {
      tableData: [
      {
        enId: '2016-05-02',
        graduateId: '王小虎',
        rpPhase: '上海市普陀区金沙江路 1518 弄'
      }]
    }
  },


}
</script>
